{"data":{"markdownRemark":null,"npmPackage":{"name":"gatsby-remark-a11y-emoji","description":"Gatsby Plugin to make Emoji in Markdown accessible. Wraps Emoji in a &lt;span&gt;-Tag with role and aria-labelledby attributes.","keywords":["gatsby","gatsby-plugin","remark","emoji","a11y"],"lastPublisher":{"name":"florianeckerstorfer","avatar":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/eab0f0d42556979629d191ef6c471b5d"},"repository":null,"readme":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"gatsby-remark-a11y-emoji\"><a href=\"#gatsby-remark-a11y-emoji\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>gatsby-remark-a11y-emoji</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Gatsby Plugin to make Emoji in Markdown accessible. Wraps Emoji in a <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;span&gt;</code>-Tag with <code class=\"language-text\">role</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">aria-labelledby</code> attributes.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>By <a href=\"https://florian.ec\">Florian Eckerstorfer</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"idea\"><a href=\"#idea\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Idea</h2>\n<p>Everyone loves emoji ðŸ’¯ðŸŽ‰ðŸ”¥, but if you use <a href=\"https://github.com/evcohen/eslint-plugin-jsx-a11y\">eslint-plugin-jsx-a11y</a> to check the accessibility of your JSX you probably know that Emoji need special handling to become accessible. Instead of just writing the emoji, you need to wrap it in a <code class=\"language-text\">span</code> and add <code class=\"language-text\">role=&quot;img&quot;</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">aria-labelledby</code> attributes.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\">\n      <pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">Gatsby is ðŸ’¯</code></pre>\n      </div>\n<p>will turn into</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\">\n      <pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">Gatsby is &lt;span role=&quot;img&quot; aria-labelledby=&quot;hundred points&quot;&gt;ðŸ’¯&lt;/span&gt;</code></pre>\n      </div>\n<h2 id=\"installation\"><a href=\"#installation\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Installation</h2>\n<p>First install the plugin with NPM or Yarn:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\">\n      <pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">npm install --save gatsby-remark-a11y-emoji</code></pre>\n      </div>\n<p>Add the plugin to <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-config.js</code>. Since <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-remark-a11y-emoji</code> converts Remark <em>text</em> nodes into <em>html</em> nodes,\nI recommend placing it at the very end of the plugins list.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\">\n      <pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">module.exports = {\n  // ...\n  plugins: [\n    {\n      resolve: `gatsby-transformer-remark`,\n      options: {\n        plugins: [\n          // ...\n          &#39;gatsby-remark-a11y-emoji&#39;,\n        ],\n      },\n    },\n  ],\n};</code></pre>\n      </div>","timeToRead":1}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/packages/gatsby-remark-a11y-emoji/","id":"02cc0338-e6d2-5521-9904-5c65b85dd5d1"}}